OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FReporter James Webster has been to
OL,7,Fmeet Flick Williams, a wheelchair user
OL,8,Ffrom York, who has been speaking out
OL,9,Fabout the issues she has faced with
OL,10,Fdoors on supermarket fridges
OL,12,FA wheelchair user from York has been
OL,13,Fspeaking out about the difficulties
OL,14,Fshe has encountered using new doors on
OL,15,Fsupermarket fridges, saying they are
OL,16,Fmaking her "dependant on other people"
OL,17,Fin a way she does not need to be.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
