OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FThey include wheelchair users not
OL,7,Fbeing able to reach some of the door
OL,8,Fhandles, the doors hitting
OL,9,Fwheelchairs, and the aisles becoming
OL,10,Ftoo narrow if two doors are open
OL,11,Fopposite each other.
OL,13,FThey have also brought up difficulties
OL,14,Ffaced by those who are visually
OL,15,Fimpaired, reporting reflections on the
OL,16,Fdoors can also make it hard for people
OL,17,Fto see through them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
