OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FTom Holder, from the British Retail
OL,7,FConsortium, said: "It's one of those
OL,8,Fkey methods that will be needed in the
OL,9,Fbid to reach net zero by 2040 and
OL,10,Findeed net zero on energy use by 2030.
OL,12,F"Doors are put in place as a fairly
OL,13,Fenergy-efficient solution to try and
OL,14,Fkeep that energy and make sure that
OL,15,Fwe're not wasting energy every time we
OL,16,Fleave these fridges on."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
